WEBVTT

00:00.918 --> 00:01.995
Previously on "Empire"...

00:02.019 --> 00:03.718
The Feds are coming for Empire.

00:03.719 --> 00:05.096
We need the evidence on Damon Cross

00:05.120 --> 00:06.431
to clear Pop's name.

00:06.455 --> 00:10.017
You realize you have
signed us a silent singer?

00:10.018 --> 00:11.855
But you and I...

00:11.856 --> 00:14.501
I just have this feeling
that we are destined to be.

00:14.525 --> 00:15.502
Hi, Daddy.

00:15.526 --> 00:17.237
Hey, sweetheart. You good?

00:20.731 --> 00:21.942
Where's my gig?

00:21.966 --> 00:23.610
Son of a bitch!

00:23.634 --> 00:25.679
You're gonna kill who?

