00:37.414 --> 00:40.393
When you build an empire...

00:40.417 --> 00:44.397
you create lots of enemies.

00:44.421 --> 00:48.735
And every single one of them
has a reason for killing you.

00:50.494 --> 00:52.405
I just did the final
walk-through, Mr. Beretti.

00:52.429 --> 00:54.040
The house is totally empty.

00:54.064 --> 00:55.809
No kidding.

00:55.833 --> 00:57.878
The bankruptcy court sold everything.

00:57.902 --> 01:01.081
Except for this.
I found it in the garage.

01:10.381 --> 01:11.892
In our business,

01:11.916 --> 01:15.428
a gold record is the ultimate
symbol of success, Beretti,

01:15.452 --> 01:16.897
so...

01:16.921 --> 01:18.899
Congratulations, Billy.

01:18.923 --> 01:20.066
Gives me chills.

01:20.090 --> 01:21.668
But with a chart-topping
banger like that,

01:21.692 --> 01:23.003
I'll take a check.

01:23.027 --> 01:25.438
Or a wire transfer,
whatever you do these days.

01:25.462 --> 01:26.606
Neither.

01:26.630 --> 01:28.842
Okay, cash.

01:28.866 --> 01:30.010
OG style.

01:30.034 --> 01:31.645
Who doesn't love the mean green?

01:31.669 --> 01:33.747
Why would I pay you cash

01:33.771 --> 01:37.551
for an artist that's
exclusively signed to my label?

01:37.575 --> 01:38.919
Since when?

01:38.943 --> 01:41.388
Since you didn't
re-sign her contract and I did.

01:41.412 --> 01:43.123
Oh, come on, Lucious.

01:43.147 --> 01:45.058
I invested a lot of money
in that girl.

01:45.082 --> 01:47.260
I bought her new hair, new D-cups.

01:47.284 --> 01:48.361
I got her off coke.

01:48.385 --> 01:49.829
And then you sneak in,

01:49.853 --> 01:51.464
sign her out from under me
in the middle of the night?

01:51.488 --> 01:54.768
It's not the same thing
you did with Kid Fo Fo?

01:54.792 --> 01:56.369
Come on, Lucious.

01:56.393 --> 01:58.538
You know I've been on
hard times for a couple years.

01:58.562 --> 02:00.840
Give me my money,
help me get back on my feet.

02:00.864 --> 02:03.810
See, that's the difference
between you and me.

02:03.834 --> 02:07.781
I genuinely care about
the artists and the music,

02:07.805 --> 02:10.083
where you only care about the money.

02:10.107 --> 02:11.918
So all you get is this plaque.

02:11.942 --> 02:13.520
Now get the hell out of my office.

02:13.544 --> 02:15.021
That's how you want to play it?

02:15.045 --> 02:16.990
Isn't that how you taught me?

02:17.014 --> 02:18.825
Oh...

02:18.849 --> 02:21.528
my lawyer's gonna be
so far up your ass.

02:22.753 --> 02:24.297
Hang it on your wall.

02:24.321 --> 02:27.500
It'll remind you of who
schooled your greedy ass.

02:41.217 --> 02:46.841
