02:48.596 --> 02:50.259
You ghost me for six months,

02:50.260 --> 02:52.005
then you show up at my crib
talking trash?

02:52.029 --> 02:53.673
I don't owe you a damn thing.

02:53.697 --> 02:56.409
I have been up nights for six months

02:56.433 --> 02:58.278
because it has been haunting me,

02:58.302 --> 03:00.680
and I've been thinking
about everything,

03:00.704 --> 03:04.751
everything that happened,
a million times.

03:04.775 --> 03:07.921
Nah, you owe me some damn answers.

